"calculation": "Project Safe asset payoffs at t=1:\n- Good: 160.\n- Bad: 120.\nExpected payoff = 0.5 * 160 + 0.5 * 120 = 140.\nFirm value:\n  V_safe = 140 / 1.10 ≈ 127.27.\n\nDebt payoffs (face 120):\n- Good: 120.\n- Bad: 120.\n=> Debt is risk-free here.\nDebt value:\n  P_D_safe = 120 / 1.10 ≈ 109.09.\n\nEquity payoffs:\n- Good: 160 − 120 = 40.\n- Bad: 120 − 120 = 0.\nEquity value:\n  P_E_safe = [0.5 * 40 + 0.5 * 0] / 1.10 = 20 / 1.10 ≈ 18.18.",
